com.ibm.team.scm.common
Interface IScmProcessConfiguration

public interface IScmProcessConfiguration

Process related configuration data for SCM operations. Operation constants are used to identify the operation the SCM component is running to the repository allowing operation based configurations for permission and participation. Repository permissions are used to control permissions for operations which don't run in the context of a project.

Since:
0.5
